      * Varible for
     D WSUSER          S             10
     D JSONstring      S          32000
     D Error           S            150
     D WN              S             15

      *get input-string
      /copy syspeds/qrpgsrcpy,prolog3

      * Parse input
     C                   EXSR      Parse
      * Open files etc
     C                   EXSR      INIT
      *
